    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "God does not own the pleasure seeker as His follower. Those only who are self-denying and who live lives of sobriety, humility, and holiness are true followers of Jesus. And such cannot enjoy the frivolous, empty conversation of the lover of the world.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">14<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"CT 327.1\" data-link=\"23.1596\">Counsels to Teachers, Parents, and Students, 327, 328</span>.</span></a></sup>",
